body:
This Shared Residential Tenancy Agreement is entered into on {{lease.start_date}} between:

LANDLORD: {{landlord.name}}
Address: {{landlord.address}}
Phone: {{landlord.phone}}
Email: {{landlord.email}}

TENANT(S):
{{tenant.primary.name}} (Primary Tenant)
{{tenant.secondary.name}} (Co-Tenant)
{{additional_tenants}}

for the shared rental of the premises described herein.

RENTAL PREMISES:
Address: {{property.address}}
Suburb: {{property.suburb}}
State: {{property.state}}
Postcode: {{property.postcode}}

Property Details:
- Property Type: {{property.type}}
- Bedrooms: {{property.bedrooms}}
- Bathrooms: {{property.bathrooms}}
- Parking Spaces: {{property.parking}}
- Garden/Yard: {{property.garden}}
- Furnished: {{property.furnished}}

The premises include all fixtures and fittings as detailed in the inventory attached as Schedule A.

INDIVIDUAL ROOM ASSIGNMENTS:

Primary Tenant ({{tenant.primary.name}}):
- Room: {{tenant.primary.room}}
- Private Bathroom: {{tenant.primary.ensuite}}
- Rent Portion: {{tenant.primary.rent_portion}}

Co-Tenant ({{tenant.secondary.name}}):
- Room: {{tenant.secondary.room}}
- Private Bathroom: {{tenant.secondary.ensuite}}
- Rent Portion: {{tenant.secondary.rent_portion}}

SHARED SPACES:
- Kitchen, living room, dining area
- Laundry facilities
- Common bathrooms (if applicable)
- Garden/outdoor areas
- Storage areas: {{shared.storage}}

All tenants have equal access to shared spaces and facilities.

RENTAL DETAILS:

Total Weekly Rent: ${{total_rent}} per week
Payment Distribution:
- {{tenant.primary.name}}: ${{tenant.primary.weekly_rent}} ({{tenant.primary.percentage}}%)
- {{tenant.secondary.name}}: ${{tenant.secondary.weekly_rent}} ({{tenant.secondary.percentage}}%)

Payment Terms:
- Payment Method: {{payment_method}}
- Payment Due: {{payment_due_date}} of each {{payment_frequency}}
- Late Payment Fee: ${{late_fee}} after {{grace_period}} days
- Bank Details: {{bank_details}}

BOND DEPOSIT:
Total Bond: ${{total_bond}}
Primary Tenant: ${{tenant.primary.bond}}
Co-Tenant: ${{tenant.secondary.bond}}

Bond held by: {{bond_authority}}

UTILITY ARRANGEMENTS:

Included in Rent:
{{utilities_included}}

Tenant Responsibility (Split Equally):
- Electricity: {{electricity_split}}
- Gas: {{gas_split}}
- Water usage charges: {{water_split}}
- Internet: {{internet_split}}
- Telephone: {{phone_split}}

Shared Household Expenses:
- Cleaning supplies: Split equally
- Garden maintenance: {{garden_responsibility}}
- Common area supplies: Split equally

Utility Connection:
- Primary tenant responsible for: {{primary_utilities}}
- Co-tenant responsible for: {{secondary_utilities}}

All utility bills must be shared within {{bill_sharing_period}} days of receipt.

HOUSE RULES FOR HARMONIOUS SHARED LIVING:

Quiet Hours: {{quiet_hours}}
Guests Policy:
- Overnight guests: {{overnight_guest_policy}}
- Maximum guest duration: {{max_guest_stay}}
- Guest notification: {{guest_notice_period}}

Cleaning Responsibilities:
- Kitchen: {{kitchen_cleaning_roster}}
- Bathrooms: {{bathroom_cleaning_roster}}
- Common areas: {{common_area_cleaning}}
- Individual rooms: Tenant responsibility

Shared Equipment Use:
- Washing machine: {{laundry_schedule}}
- Kitchen appliances: {{kitchen_usage_rules}}
- TV/Entertainment: {{entertainment_rules}}

Parking:
- Primary Tenant: {{primary_parking}}
- Co-Tenant: {{secondary_parking}}
- Visitor parking: {{visitor_parking}}

Smoking Policy: {{smoking_policy}}
Pet Policy: {{pet_policy}}

MAINTENANCE RESPONSIBILITIES:

Landlord Responsibilities:
- Structural repairs and maintenance
- Major appliance repairs (over ${{major_repair_threshold}})
- Plumbing and electrical issues
- Heating/cooling system maintenance
- Garden maintenance (if specified): {{landlord_garden_duty}}

Tenant Responsibilities:
- General cleanliness and hygiene
- Minor repairs under ${{minor_repair_limit}}
- Light bulb replacement
- Battery replacement (smoke detectors, etc.)
- Garden maintenance (if specified): {{tenant_garden_duty}}

Emergency Repairs:
- Contact landlord immediately: {{emergency_contact}}
- Emergency repair authority: ${{emergency_repair_limit}}
- After-hours emergency service: {{emergency_service}}

Repair Request Process:
1. Submit written request to landlord
2. Include photos if applicable
3. Response timeframe: {{repair_response_time}}
4. Urgent repairs: {{urgent_repair_timeframe}}

INSURANCE REQUIREMENTS:

Landlord Insurance:
- Building insurance: Landlord responsibility
- Landlord protection insurance: {{landlord_insurance}}
- Public liability: {{public_liability_coverage}}

Tenant Insurance (Highly Recommended):
- Contents insurance for personal belongings
- Public liability coverage
- Temporary accommodation coverage

Liability and Damage:
- Tenants jointly and severally liable for damage
- Individual liability for damage to assigned room: Individual tenant
- Shared space damage: {{shared_damage_liability}}
- Normal wear and tear: Landlord responsibility

Security:
- Security deposit: ${{security_deposit}}
- Key deposit: ${{key_deposit}} per set
- Alarm code responsibility: {{alarm_responsibility}}
- Lost key replacement: {{key_replacement_fee}}

DISPUTE RESOLUTION PROCESS:

Between Tenants:
1. Direct communication and negotiation
2. Mediation through {{tenant_mediation_service}}
3. Seek advice from tenancy advocacy services
4. Legal proceedings if necessary

Tenant-Landlord Disputes:
1. Written complaint to landlord
2. Mediation through {{tenancy_tribunal}}
3. Application to tenancy tribunal
4. Appeal processes as available

Emergency Contacts:
- Landlord: {{landlord_emergency}}
- Property Manager: {{property_manager}}
- Emergency Repairs: {{emergency_repairs}}
- Tenancy Advice: {{tenancy_advice_service}}

Legal Compliance:
- Agreement complies with {{tenancy_act}}
- Jurisdiction: {{court_jurisdiction}}
- Consumer protection laws apply
- Fair trading legislation applies

Record Keeping:
- All communications in writing
- Photo evidence for disputes
- Keep copies of all payments
- Maintain inspection records
